====Usage notes====
The past of broadcast is either ''broadcast'' or ''broadcasted''. Both are in use, but ''broadcast'' is much more common, especially in the simple past but also as past participle. As of 2019, Google Books search gives 326,000 results for [http://www.google.com/search?tbm=bks&tbo=1&q=%2B%22was+broadcast%22&btnG=Search+Books "was broadcast"], vs. 12,900 for [http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&tbo=1&tbm=bks&q=%2B%22was+broadcasted%22&aq=f&aqi=&aql=&oq= "was broadcasted"].

